text: The Rimosus Sphinx (Isognathus rimosa) is a moth of the Sphingidae family. It lives in tropical climates from northern Brazil north through Central America, the West Indies and Mexico to southern Arizona. The wingspan is 70-102 mm. ==References== ==Other websites== *Life Cycle *Butterflies and Moths of North America Category:Sphingidae
